quran[38]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,Patichitendekwa chakutendekwa (Kiyama)
  56,2,Pangali jwakanila yakutendekwa kwakwe
  56,3,(Chalakwe ni) chakwaatulusya (achimakafili pakwajinjisya ku Moto) ni kwakwesya (Asilamu pakwajinjisya ku Mbepo)
  56,4,Ndema jalichitenganyika litaka kutenganyika kwamachili
  56,5,Matumbi ni kusyajidwa-syajidwa
  56,6,Ni kuŵa luwundu lyakuwululusyidwa
  56,7,Ni tinchiŵa jenumanja (pa Kiyama) mikutula jitatu
  56,8,"Basi (pachiŵa pana) ŵandu ŵa kunkono wan’dyo, ana ŵandu ŵa kunkono wan’dyo ni ŵapi (uchimbichimbi wao uchiŵa uli)"
  56,9,"Ni (pachiŵa pana soni) ŵandu ŵa kunkono wanchiji, ana ŵandu ŵa kunkono wanchiji ni ŵapi (kusakala kwao kuchiŵa uli)"
  56,10,Ni (pachiŵa pana soni) ŵaŵalongolele (pakutenda yambone ku duniya) ŵatachiŵa ŵakulongolela (ku Mbepo)
  56,11,Ŵanganyao ni ŵatachiŵa ŵakuŵandichisyidwa (kwa Allah)
  56,12,Tachiŵa m’Matimbe Gachindimba (ku Mbepo)
  56,13,Likuga lyejinji (lya akulongolela ku yambone) lichiŵa lyakutyochela mu ŵandu ŵandanda
  56,14,Sano (likuga) lyannono (lya akulongolela ku yambone) lichiŵa lyakutyochela mu ŵandu ŵakumalichisya
  56,15,Ali pa itengu yauchimbichimbi yeluche (ni golodi ni mitapo jine)
  56,16,Tachiyijegamaga mwakulolegana
  56,17,Tachasyungulaga (pa kwatumichila) achachanda ŵakutamilichika (pa uchanda)
  56,18,"Ni migao kwisa soni mabilika (ga yakumwa), ni ipanda ya ukana wakuumila mu tutumule jwakujilimaga"
  56,19,Ngasalwala nao ntwe namuno kutyoka lunda
  56,20,Ni isogosi iliyose yatakaisaguleje
  56,21,Ni nyama ja ijuni jatakajilaluchileje
  56,22,Ni achimmasyeto ŵameso gakulanguka soni gekulungwa mwakusalalila
  56,23,(Ŵakuswejela) nti chisawu ngalekale syesunjidwe
  56,24,Kuŵa malipilo pa yaŵaliji nkupanganya
  56,25,"Ngaaja kupikana mwalakwemo maloŵe gangali mate, namuno gakutendekasya kupata sambi"
  56,26,"Ikaŵeje maloŵe ganti: Ntendele, ntendele"
  56,27,"Sano (pachiŵa pana) ŵandu ŵa kunkono wan’dyo, ana ŵandu ŵa kunkono wan’dyo ni ŵapi (uchimbichimbi wao uchiŵa uli)"
  56,28,(Tachiŵa) mu itela ya masaawu yetyosye miŵa
  56,29,Ni itela ya magombo yesogole magombo gakwe mwakusajikana chenene
  56,30,Ni miwulili jakwendelechela
  56,31,Ni mesi gakujilima ndaŵi ni katema
  56,32,Ni isogosi yejinji
  56,33,Yangakatichisya kasogole nambo soni yangasiŵiilidwa
  56,34,Ni yakutandika yenyakulidwe (pa itengu yauchimbichimbi)
  56,35,Chisimu Uwwe chitukaaguumbe ŵanganyao (achakongwe ŵakuumila ku duniya) kagumbidwe kane (kakusalala nnope kulekangana ni muŵaŵelele ku duniya)
  56,36,Basi chitukatende kuŵa ŵaali
  56,37,"Ŵakulinonyelesya kwa achalume ŵao, ŵakulandana misingu"
  56,38,(Tachiŵa) ŵa (achalume) ŵa kunkono wan’dyo